{"tid":1689904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我諗我終於知點解啲狗成日喺無人嘅地方放催淚彈","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T05:56:40.000Z","uid":149563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1ef9e6668589256b54a5dfe47e844c60eec067","tid":1689904,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"大家都知中國冇錢要成日靠香港偷偷地科水<br />\n而向中國買催淚彈亦都係其中一個途徑科水比佢哋<br />\n之前舊嗰啲未用晒就好難買中國貨<br />\n所以咪係咁放希望快啲用晒啲倉底貨<br />\n到而家用中國tg就更加要清快啲，清完又可以幫中國買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁當然又係用納稅人嘅錢啦<br />\n同埋佢地可能每一次都要跑數，今日要放幾多tg，要拉幾多人<br />\n尋日突然有不反對通知書都可能其實係為咗跑夠數拉人<br />\n突然咁多文宣手足比人拉都係咁解<br />\n我估"},{"pid":"2780f9a60613be4273ab705de21e471c78de19ba","tid":1689904,"uid":262146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaWoJsy.png&h=16518c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQwSkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQwSkW.png&h=766c26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLR4sUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLR4sUj.png&h=1dd0aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nShare:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/3162303350510828?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F454004001340790%2Fposts%2F3162303350510828%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=d402614d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/3162303350510828?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\nRT:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/effygrande1/status/1190670210027552768?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feffygrande1%2Fstatus%2F1190670210027552768%3Fs%3D21&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=8abdae0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feffygrande1%2Fstatus%2F1190670210027552768%3Fs%3D21&h=113297e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/effygrande1/status/1190670210027552768?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n死黑警從來無認真關心過香港人條命<br />\n講緊被死亡個案，佢仲係度冷笑、當笑話"},{"pid":"7a6511beb2a3b657843ede3bf3f660bb50ab4415","tid":1689904,"uid":35186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"同意係為左跑數所以濫捕，但濫捕既原意係為左製造恐慌既情緒。<br />\n<br />\n但科水比中共呢個point講得再白啲，應該係向大陸買賣軍火個陣，造就機會比狗同大陸從中掠水。"},{"pid":"1f0b2f321b7477735e1c857f4e4f74b543f4dc59","tid":1689904,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"你啲tg 賣到幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90f9b1829d1eff187e20a7c7c2d6da5f0c040fb","tid":1689904,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"中後排可唔可以click入黎睇睇 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到黎可唔可以緊張少少 審時度勢..<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}